  "body": "When I'm using hardhat 2.8.0, I can use both below commands:\r\n```bash\r\nyarn test test/protocol/MatrixValuer.test.js\r\nyarn test ./test/protocol/MatrixValuer.test.js\r\n```\r\nAfter upgrade to 2.8.1 or 2.8.2, only `yarn test test/protocol/MatrixValuer.test.js` can work, \r\n```text\r\nhardhat test test/protocol/MatrixValuer.test.js\r\n......\r\n  6 passing (4s)\r\nDone in 6.70s.\r\n\r\nyarn test ./test/protocol/MatrixValuer.test.js\r\nyarn run v1.22.17\r\n```\r\n\r\nBut `yarn test ./test/protocol/MatrixValuer.test.js` reports below error:\r\n```text\r\nhardhat test ./test/protocol/MatrixValuer.test.js\r\n......\r\n  6 passing (4s)\r\n\r\nAn unexpected error occurred:\r\n\r\nError: Cannot find module './test/protocol/MatrixValuer.test.js'\r\nRequire stack:\r\n- MY_PROJECT_DIR/node_modules/mocha/lib/mocha.js\r\n- MY_PROJECT_DIR/node_modules/mocha/index.js\r\n- MY_PROJECT_DIR/node_modules/hardhat/builtin-tasks/test.js\r\n- MY_PROJECT_DIR/node_modules/hardhat/internal/core/tasks/builtin-tasks.js\r\n- MY_PROJECT_DIR/node_modules/hardhat/internal/core/config/config-loading.js\r\n- MY_PROJECT_DIR/node_modules/hardhat/internal/cli/cli.js\r\n    at Function.Module._resolveFilename (node:internal/modules/cjs/loader:933:15)\r\n    at Function.resolve (node:internal/modules/cjs/helpers:108:19)\r\n    at Function.Mocha.unloadFile (MY_PROJECT_DIR/node_modules/mocha/lib/mocha.js:407:32)\r\n    at MY_PROJECT_DIR/node_modules/mocha/lib/mocha.js:435:11\r\n    at Array.forEach (<anonymous>)\r\n    at Mocha.unloadFiles (MY_PROJECT_DIR/node_modules/mocha/lib/mocha.js:434:14)\r\n    at Mocha.dispose (MY_PROJECT_DIR/node_modules/mocha/lib/mocha.js:581:8)\r\n    at SimpleTaskDefinition.action (MY_PROJECT_DIR/node_modules/hardhat/src/builtin-tasks/test.ts:60:11)\r\n    at runMicrotasks (<anonymous>)\r\n    at processTicksAndRejections (node:internal/process/task_queues:96:5) {\r\n  code: 'MODULE_NOT_FOUND',\r\n  requireStack: [\r\n    'MY_PROJECT_DIR/node_modules/mocha/lib/mocha.js',\r\n    'MY_PROJECT_DIR/node_modules/mocha/index.js',\r\n    'MY_PROJECT_DIR/node_modules/hardhat/builtin-tasks/test.js',\r\n    'MY_PROJECT_DIR/node_modules/hardhat/internal/core/tasks/builtin-tasks.js',\r\n    'MY_PROJECT_DIR/node_modules/hardhat/internal/core/config/config-loading.js',\r\n    'MY_PROJECT_DIR/node_modules/hardhat/internal/cli/cli.js'\r\n  ]\r\n}\r\nerror Command failed with exit code 1.\r\n```",
